windowtolayer (0.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian/Ubuntu package of the upstream windowtolayer release,
    distributed via this repo's GitHub Releases alongside swaylock-plugin.
  * Like the COPR package, the build tracks the latest upstream stable tag:
    contrib/debian-windowtolayer/fetch-source.sh resolves it at build time
    and prepends a changelog entry when it is newer than this one.

